metadata.name: Golden Straw VIP Mintpass - Moon
metadata.description: This is a hand-selected exclusive Royal Membership of 400 NFT enthusiasts, ambassadors, and NFT project founders. As a Juice Spaces Royal, you design, build and support your very own NFT project together with some of the leading minds in the NFT space. Additionally, the Golden Straw VIP Mintpass holders receive guaranteed access to all Juice Spaces NFT projects.
